	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Im not gonna answer this poll because it all depends upon the group.<br />
Obviously your group was not an NBG group and so its fair for whoever won the roll to do with the item what they will.<br />
Personally I will never roll for an item I cant use or that I feel would be more useful to another member of the group. Ill say something like "that item is great for you MT, I wont roll"....usually then most others will agree and hold off as well, unless they really can use it.<br />
Once I rolled for an item because another person in the group rolled and didnt need the item. I rolled, won the item and gave it to the group member that did need it <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="Smile"></font></p>
	
	<p><p><img src="/forums/images/sig_separator.gif" width="282" height="11" Alt="Hey! Watch where you point that thing!"><br>
