	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">I don't roll on lore items I already possess... It seems rude to ask someone else to carry a Lore Item because one already possesses it. I have more then enough stuff hoarded for my alts, let alone asking someone who might have used the item to carry it for me so i can twink my already twinked enogh alts lol...<br />
Most of the time the looting goes Need Before Greed (for the present characters) in the groups I am in and if no one needs the item as an upgrade it's open roll to do with what you wish.</font></p>
	
